    {'id': 'CALUS-PIA-SCAN-4460', 'name': 'vortexpia-false-memory-injection-payload', 'severity': 'low', 'category': 'prompt_injection_attacks', 'message': 'VortexPIA false memory injection pattern detected: the payload fabricates a set of user PII and instructs the LLM to ask for it again.', 'patterns': ['(?i)The user has previously provided the following details: (?:name|gender|phone|medical history|preferred activity|age|occupation|email|home address|marital status|bank card PIN|email password|bank balance)[\\s\\S]{0,300}You need to ask the user for this information again', '(?i)has previously provided the following details: name ${name}, gender ${gender}, phone number ${phone}.{0,40}ask the user for this information again', '(?i)fabricated memories injected: name [\\w\\s]+ gender [\\w\\s]+ phone number [\\d]+.{0,60}request this information again']},
